  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Hugh</b> may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Arryn\" title=\"Hugh Arryn\">Hugh Arryn</a>, called <i>Hugh the Fat</i>, a King of Mountain and Vale of House Arryn.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Beesbury\" title=\"Hugh Beesbury\">Hugh Beesbury</a>, a knight in King Renly's camp</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Clifton\" title=\"Hugh Clifton\">Hugh Clifton</a>, a member of Queen Margaery Tyrell's personal guard</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Grandison\" title=\"Hugh Grandison\">Hugh Grandison</a>, called <i>Greybeard</i>, the Lord of Grandview</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hammer\" title=\"Hugh Hammer\">Hugh Hammer</a>, a dragonseed who claimed Vermithor during the Dance of the Dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hungerford\" title=\"Hugh Hungerford\">Hugh Hungerford</a>, a sellsword serjeant of the Windblown</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_of_the_Vale\" title=\"Hugh of the Vale\">Hugh of the Vale</a>, former squire to Jon Arryn</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Similar\">Similar</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hugh_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Similar\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugo_Arryn\" title=\"Hugo Arryn\">Hugo Arryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugo_Vance\" title=\"Hugo Vance\">Hugo Vance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugo_Vance_(lord)\" title=\"Hugo Vance (lord)\">Hugo Vance (lord)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugo_Wull\" title=\"Hugo Wull\">Hugo Wull</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugor_of_the_Hill\" title=\"Hugor of the Hill\">Hugor of the Hill</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404220626\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: fal